      "type": "Default",
      "timestamp": "2025-08-22T06:28:52.491+00:00",
      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "You can create a custom padring using the [leo/padring](https://github.com/librelane/librelane/tree/leo/padring) (experimental) branch in LibreLane. I had a setup for gf180mcu lying around somewhere, will have to see if I can find it again.",
      "author": {
